<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَإِذَا السَّماءُ كُشِطَتْ <span class="c2">(١١)</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>